240
00:13:56,166 --> 00:13:57,625
She's the key...

241
00:13:57,708 --> 00:14:00,333
I think she'll be able to lead
us right to the Innocence...

242
00:14:00,416 --> 00:14:02,833
We're sure lucky I found her.

243
00:14:02,916 --> 00:14:04,000
Yeah right...

244
00:14:04,083 --> 00:14:07,791
So how are your
investigation's going?

245
00:14:07,875 --> 00:14:10,708
It looks like my brother's
theory is correct after all...

246
00:14:10,791 --> 00:14:12,333
so... right after I
split with you...

247
00:14:12,416 --> 00:14:14,833
I attempted to leave the town.

248
00:14:18,416 --> 00:14:20,333
When I walked through
the edge of the village,

249
00:14:20,416 --> 00:14:22,833
it just spit me right back in.

250
00:14:22,916 --> 00:14:25,166
So... it's just as we feared.

251
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:26,750
Now we're stuck
in this endless loop

252
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:29,791
of a town along with everyone
else until we find a solution.

253
00:14:29,875 --> 00:14:32,750
That's why we need to
get the Innocence ASAP.

254
00:14:32,833 --> 00:14:34,375
Innocence?

255
00:14:36,291 --> 00:14:39,250
That's her, Lenalee!
She's the one!

256
00:14:39,333 --> 00:14:46,125
Wait! I'm sorry I screamed!

257
00:14:46,208 --> 00:14:47,750
You're Exorcists?

258
00:14:47,833 --> 00:14:50,250
We are, but why are
you running away?

259
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:52,291
We're here to help you.

260
00:14:52,375 --> 00:14:53,625
I'm sorry...

261
00:14:53,708 --> 00:14:55,833
I've been through a lot lately.

262
00:14:59,958 --> 00:15:01,208
Yeah, hello...?

263
00:15:01,291 --> 00:15:02,666
